tags.description: This is actually all to the North of the main line of the road and is actually a quadrilateral with one non-square side.  It extends to the end of the adopted part of the road.
tags.note: Originally mapped as an area (237210065)  sharing a common Northern edge.  Rendered well in the standard rendering, but had objections to apparent loops confusing routing algorithms.  Area retained with no main tags. North edge moved centre to kerb.

tags.description: Island with lighted bollards and single tall beacon.  Dropped and tactile kerbs. Tactile refuge.
